    {
      "id": "ad0e0ff1-f929-4eae-97ac-7a3db862e58b_616a8413-d85a-4073-a590-a3de034e4989",
      "label": "Why do you want to join Lovable specifically and what makes you a great fit?",
      "type": "textarea",
      "required": true,
      "value": "I'm excited about the opportunity to work at Lovable because I'm drawn to organizations that operate at scale, solve complex technical challenges, and prioritize innovation and long-term impact. Throughout my experience at Microsoft and Amazon Robotics, I've enjoyed working at the intersection of technology, operations, and strategy — leading cross-functional initiatives, building scalable systems, and driving measurable business outcomes.\n\nWhat particularly interests me about Lovable is the opportunity to contribute to high-impact products and programs while collaborating with talented teams across engineering, product, and business functions. I'm especially motivated by environments where I can combine technical depth with program leadership to improve reliability, automation, and operational efficiency.\n\nIn my current role, I've led large-scale resilience and automation initiatives, developed AI-driven workflow solutions, and managed complex cross-organizational programs under executive visibility. I enjoy taking ambiguous problems, creating structure, and driving execution from concept through delivery. I'd be excited to bring that same mindset to Lovable while continuing to grow in a fast-paced and innovative environment.\n\nBeyond the technical challenges, I'm also looking for a company whose culture emphasizes ownership, collaboration, and continuous improvement. From what I've seen, Lovable aligns strongly with those values, which makes the opportunity especially compelling to me.",
      "source": "why-company-template.md (substituted [Company]='Lovable')",
      "status": "filled",
      "matched_rule": "why_company_essay",
      "options": null,
      "_ashby_type": "LongText",
      "_ashby_id": "ad0e0ff1-f929-4eae-97ac-7a3db862e58b_616a8413-d85a-4073-a590-a3de034e4989"
    },
